    "title": "Forensic Ledger: Immutable Audit Trails for Deterministic Intelligent Systems",
    "publication_date": "2026-04-24",
    "description": "The Forensic Ledger defines the immutable, cryptographically-signed audit trail architecture for deterministic intelligent systems. Every reasoning step, decision, constraint evaluation, and environmental interaction is recorded in an append-only ledger with forensic integrity. This paper specifies the ledger data structures, signature schemes, chain integrity mechanisms, and compliance verification procedures for post-hoc accountability in regulated AI deployments.",
